w_JcceCqPXpX7pIlM9XLKn92eJ0bpLzEOf__Cd1cPIJ7bXBU8-MX8OsMnPNsyzLDdxgof6q2QERhXQbn9WnyhjmPpYx507edSBaQiYcptQHtv63vK16x4rapq8Fuh6gfTh3Z5aS94ix7rNFuP6cGdrCtRcdRyvv-nNVwBtGVhz_IQRZ8G59rbqRA_3bK6asukhfUwa-XgEWRE4kU6D70ytD4RN65fLrtr415aSqghOr0jF8573DApCMYxqBYtcEjqmfhJSsIwn4kv7LLzaDg__-BrFoztMRw","width":720,"height":1080,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/102862944552058111605\">Can Ramonet</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN0igDWOdnADEGrGGtbd_xf0jDhIpsVgVNjGssF_Y2ThcnyXV48ey95hwTsN0G0jy5KzPFVMnV5EzYAln9Gt5mOqM5ItfiT9XLsMU6cfU5tHnQdYXh0ovTMQbu8BHYbWleCEAzZd3nVj3OnFD4_ks1MVa1Souqs0S9hwvCXbmMbIbZwyDcheCq_YJfbutPzrm6YKOl9brMcd2wS1zFMdWG8ZXkzb24-Q8dcKqliqzs8QqU3KhdvJq3-PDPpwIwtwbO8R-yIpNSiA1Y9dHxu0_j7zoHVC6HCslgG6Pt0fxNpgOA","width":1080,"height":570,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/102862944552058111605\">Can Ramonet</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"Isabella Faarborg","rating":5,"text":"We had our wedding at Can Ramonet, and we wanna thank every single person who made it possible - especially Erica, Inma & the chef. Everything was perfect, down to the last detail, they did last minute menu changes, without any problems, they attended our every need, they made sure I had a bridal bouquet & the special flowers i wanted.\nWe stayed 31 people & everybody was happy & well taken care of. - it has 3 houses with several rooms, 3 shared kitchens, a large pool & outdoor area - BEAUTIFUL surroundings, wine yards for miles & miles.\nWe brought our dog, and we loved how the people of can Ramonet cared for her & made sure she was okay.\nThe rooms are spacious, rustic, and well taken care of, the whole place have so much soul. We loved any minute of the weekend, only sad thing is that it’s over. We’re hoping to come back to a reunion someday.  ❤️","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Pol Baldrich Sala","rating":5,"text":"The weekend was perfect. The service was so great. The place is so beautiful and the weeding was so funny. All the waiters were amazing and all the time making you feel welcome. The family running the place knows how to feel welcome","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"gerry sequeira","rating":3,"text":"Okay rustic place. No soap or gel or shampoo in the bathroom. Had to bring our own coffee. Old stove with gas tanks , difficult to light. Nice sized party room (though no sink). Nice pool. A bit pricey given above.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Oliver Hvidt","rating":5,"text":"Can Ramonet was the absolute dream-venue for our wedding.\n\nThe place is beyond beautiful. It is very authentic and you can feel the history, but at the same time, it has all the modern conveniences you would expect.\n\nWe had 40 people staying over the weekend and everyone were perfectly comfortable - and we had so much fun!\n\nThe surroundings are stunning - in all directions are panomaric views of rolling hills, vineyards and the Mediterranean sea on the horizon.\n\nThe place was very easy for our guests to get to. Most of our guests flew in to Barcelona airport, which is less than 30 minutes from Can Ramonet by car or taxi.\n\nThe food at Can Ramonet was delicious, both during the wedding and in the surrounding days.\n\nThe best thing about Can Ramonet, however, is Erika and her team at the villa. For more than a year leading up to the wedding, Erika was extremely helpful and flexible in planning and taking care of preparations. During the weekend, she and her team went \"above and beyond\" every day, to make sure that everyone had the perfect experience. No matter if it was a grand-parent with an allergy, or a crying baby, Erika was always there to help make sure everyone was comfortable. I don''t know how she does it!\n\nWhen we planned our wedding, we looked at 30+ venues all over Southern Europe. We''re so happy we picked Can Ramonet in the end - nothing could have better!","time":"4 years ago"},{"author":"Carlos Valdivieso","rating":5,"text":"Great place to have a birthday party, weeding or whatever meeting you want to have. Good beds (up to 30 people or a bit more) toilets are new. It''s out of town but your mobile signal works perfectly and it has a swimming pool. Great views as well!","time":"6 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
