emarkable event.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Geoffrey De Ram","rating":5,"text":"Very lovely hidden gem! We didn''t plan to get there first but found it walking. The owner is so lovely and offered us to taste several wines which were really good. We felt no pressure buying anything but ended up buying a few bottles as the wine was really good.\nThe terrasse and the view are incredible!","time":"2 years ago"},{"author":"Krisztina Gelbmann","rating":5,"text":"We had a wonderful time at Patrick`s. His wine offer was absolutely delicious and the view from there is incredible. We can only recommend!","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"anuvrat saboo","rating":5,"text":"We visited this place on a public open day, in a group of 6. The host Ignace was amaazing, and made us feel at home! We did the wine tasting there (tasted 8), and it was a fantastic experience, the views were breathtaking and so was the wine! Would definitely recommend a visit!","time":"3 years ago"},{"author":"Martin Guggemos","rating":5,"text":"This was the best wine tasting I''ve been to, it was perfect! The view is spectacular the wine was great and our host Igneca was lovely! I would definitely come here again.","time":"3 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
