he show and should have 6 stars.","time":"3 years ago"},{"author":"Swissmiss1985 Sarah","rating":3,"text":"+ wonderful clean rooms\n+ wonderful view\n+ dinner was very delicious\n- you have to pay for the spa even\nif you booked the spa rooms???\n- no ac\n- breakfast buffet is a little sad for a\n4 star hotel\n\nAll in all we expected more from a 4 star hotel...","time":"2 years ago"},{"author":"Gilles Curchod","rating":4,"text":"We went to the SPA. We were warmly welcomed by the personnel. The SPA is small but very cost with a nice swimming pool, sauna and hammam, a small patio. The ritual with scrubbing and massage was very good and relaxing. A good way to disconnect at the end of the week. And a great view when you go out after this wonderful time.\n\nIf you like my review, give it a thumb 🙂","time":"6 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
