ew weddings at this location. The location is DIVINE. Impeccably kept and well maintained, this house is full of wonderful victorian delights. A cascading stairwell, large wooden ballrooms and a beautiful terrace which opens out onto the lake of Lucerne.\n\nIt’s an absolute dream.\n\nThe catering is also spectacular, and the staff are some of the friendliest folk I have encountered in the event circuit.","time":"7 years ago"},{"author":"Pietro Catalano","rating":5,"text":"Spectacular Location, amazing Team behind. for my personal experience the Best Location in Switzerland.","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"Gerard Baron von Sachsen","rating":5,"text":"I had the wonderful opportunity to attend a party at this splendid location, somewhere end December 2017. Seldom have I seen a venue as impressive as Villa St. Charles Hall. This place breathes the atmosphere of many centuries, however, it is not that old at al: only about 100 years. The rooms are fitted with stunning taste and attention to detail. Truely a 5-star feeling. Catering was out of this world and the management and staff extremely helpful. Some keywords regarding the interior: lush, luxurious, tasteful, trendy, cool and overwhelming!","time":"7 years ago"},{"author":"Jana Chadrabova","rating":5,"text":"Very nice place....the most beautiful place for weddings I know. The place has an incredible energy. Thank you very much.","time":"a year ago"}]'::jsonb,
