d and while I was in the bathroom. They appeared to assume I had already moved rooms, yet they knocked and immediately entered without waiting for permission, which was unacceptable.\nTye premises of the hotel are beautiful and well kept. I enjoyed their spa as it was not crowded.\nOverall, the experience was quite average. Won’t come back for sure. The location is too far and not much to do around.","time":"3 weeks ago"},{"author":"Yan Xuan Lim","rating":5,"text":"Park Hotel Vitznau is beautiful! The location is serene and the facilities are well maintained. Appreciate Przemysław (restaurant staff), Alina, Laura, Nehrie & Wang Yue for giving us a pleasant stay and welcome. The breakfast was good too.\n\nThe location is great and the service/housekeeping team made the stay even better. We saw how pristine the glasses and reflective surfaces were because of the team''s effort :)","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"George Gorman","rating":5,"text":"Perfection...\nBeautiful location, luxurious spa with large selection of facilitues and heated indoor outdoor pool.\n\nAmazing professional service with can do attitude from staff, nothing they wont consider or look into for you, attentive and engaging if you seek it and allow your privacy if not.\n\nFood for breakfast, lunch and dinner amazing, with fresh and stunning presentation, then there is the next level Focus Atelier restuarant!\n\nWe stayed in the Residence suite which had stunning lake views and stylish spacious interior, this was our 20th anniversary trip and they made it very special. Thank you","time":"3 weeks ago"},{"author":"Jason Markham","rating":5,"text":"From the moment we arrived, we were greeted with genuine warmth and kindness. Every staff member we encountered was incredibly friendly, attentive, and eager to make our stay exceptional. The level of service was truly impeccable from top to bottom, thoughtful, professional, and full of heart.\n\nA special mention goes to the hotel staff drivers and front desk, who went above and beyond to make our experience memorable. They not only got us where we needed to go but also shared wonderful insights and recommendations about the area, making each day enjoyable.\n\nThis hotel stands out not just for its beauty or amenities but for the people who make it feel so welcoming. We left with smiles and wonderful memories and cannot wait to return.","time":"2 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
