S-GMcf3tzD-WCAusexCCrCesEd8yQThCj4WHu2pfGiqltYzow9PHcYJFYQS9UwIW9gdzQnx_kvW_05rMQ7d2D-tNc2lFGe1rDYmGXvlYYnDWO2YfiIV4BojnDzjRQda-tDQ","width":4000,"height":3000,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/111715661914557748015\">LeCrans</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN32odXloF5pfELydBc6srjXuVksB6E97Glf5UZZqlpjLSPY_s0_icNLWKNSGark1H3uIA4KseZSoJdYASj8JKhJdlJC4UXut0Cnn0EL4R75vwjK3iuznXtzYLgq-XAQk_6nKBtCmcb9AtBUBQS3DwBf70VYGG86X_uDxKD8gwZZGkyj-m60PfmemxI9JSvSzUNiLK7Hy4fSdDLYfuLtvCdkqwnlgJhUHz7vQb4X4Fd5PGr8xWWXL6UKYTwVhDFob6xk4WE7y2emTMlpJQCZ_V1d2N2qj8lYxyOmf3KCS8P0PQ","width":4000,"height":3000,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/111715661914557748015\">LeCrans</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"J. R.","rating":5,"text":"We truly enjoyed wonderful days at LeCrans!\nI would like to thank Stéphen at the reception, who made us feel completely at home from the moment we arrived. His attentiveness and care throughout our stay made a lasting impression.\nAdditionally, I would also like to highlight Laureen at breakfast - she was exceptionally kind and professional, embodying service excellence in every gesture.\nThe breakfast itself was also memorable. We especially loved the homemade jams and marmalade, the incredibly tasty homemade pastries, and the thoughtfully selected assortment of local cheeses and cold cuts.\nWhat a wonderful hideaway!","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"fiona mcloughlin","rating":5,"text":"A High-Level Wellness Experience\n\nFrom the moment I entered Wellness at Le Crans, a sense of quiet luxury took hold. The atmosphere was effortless yet meticulously curated — calm, composed, and flawlessly attentive.\n\nThere was nothing to manage, nothing to consider. I simply let go, enveloped in an environment where every detail was as pure and rarefied as the alpine air. Discretion was seamless; care was exacting.\n\nThe facial was exceptional — a sophisticated fusion of cutting-edge skincare technology and intuitively skilled hands. I emerged visibly renewed: glowing, weightless, and somehow restored to a younger, more vibrant version of myself.","time":"6 months ago"},{"author":"Johny M.","rating":5,"text":"We had a wonderful time in LeCrans, it''s by far the best small hotel we have stayed in so far.\n\nThe rooms are super cozy, providing a genuinely warm atmosphere with a lot of wood and other natural elements.\n\nThe restaurant is an experience on its own, we were truly impressed with the food and the staff.\n\nThe wellness area is also quite an experience, with a warm outdoor pool while the outside temperature was below zero.\n\nIt''s just perfect, and we will come back.","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"Justin Wilson","rating":2,"text":"The interior design of the hotel is exceptional, unfortunately, this is where the positives end. The service was at best a disappointment. Upon check-in, swearing could be heard from the back office, which set a very uncomfortable tone at the start of our stay. Even more unsettling was encountering staff visibly upset, crying in the hallway on another occasion as we walked back to our room. What should have been simple requests took days to be addressed, and the attitude of the staff felt cold and unhelpful. The work place culture the hotel clearly needs to be addressed.","time":"11 months ago"},{"author":"Olivier Roussel","rating":5,"text":"A wonderful hotel with all the services that you can desire.\nEverything is awesome, staff, quality, equipment,\nThe spa area and the team are astonished. So professional.\nWithout thinking about the quality of silence so high in the crans Montana area.\nExcellent ratio quality/ Price.\nWe have with my dear, every year our Christmas party 🥳🎉","time":"a year ago"}]'::jsonb,
