'[{"author":"Lyn VR","rating":5,"text":"Nice location , right on front of Brienzersee . The lady reception is quite accommodating and friendly. Easy check in . Clean and spacious enough yet outdated room. Breakfast is good by standard and the servers are quite helpful and friendly. Overall a good value for the money to stay near the center of Interlaken.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Colin Skinner","rating":5,"text":"Great hotel with excellent half board menu choices. The staff are super friendly. Great location with easy bus connections to Interlaken Ost and West. Away from the hubbub of the town.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Amna Sajid","rating":5,"text":"We got lake facing rooms and the views were awesome.The staff was super helpful.The location is great if you wish to visit the mountain attractions.There were a few options for breakfast.There was a game room for coffee and ironing clothes.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Jawahar S","rating":5,"text":"Really breathtaking views, just a walk away!\nSuch a beautiful place. Bus stop towards InterLaken is just opposite to the property. Jetty is less than 500 metres away. Breakfast included bread, spreads, juices/coffee. Kind receptionist.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Carmen Argiles","rating":4,"text":"Really beautiful views from the hotel. Very comfortable beds.\nCalm place with several restaurants, hikings and activities close around.\nReally nice receptionists who are happy to show you what to do around and help you with anything you need.\nBreakfast not amazing, but enough. Long wait to have your coffee, so get up with some time.","time":"7 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
