us and all details are thought of, plenty of space in the lobby to socialise, spa is wonderful including indoor pool with diving facilities and outdoor jacuzzi with fabulous views.","time":"3 weeks ago"},{"author":"Oleg Vladyka","rating":5,"text":"Suvretta House is a true gem in St. Moritz, offering timeless elegance, first-class service, and stunning mountain views. The atmosphere is warm and refined, the rooms are luxurious, and the dining is exceptional — a perfect place for an unforgettable stay.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Ari Derman","rating":5,"text":"My wife and I stayed at Suvretta this past March for our honeymoon and had a wonderful time. As soon as you enter the lobby, the place feels so magical and homey. Our suite was so comfortable and clean, and not to mention how amazing the luxury bathrooms were. The turn down service was special and timely. The breakfast was over the top incredible, with such a large selection and quality food. The service was impeccable. It is so convenient to ski with just steps away from a lift. The ski lockers were very comfortable too. Our favorite part, the tea time after a long day of skiing. 🫖\n\nWe highly recommend Suvretta for a luxury ski vacation. We hope to come back again soon! We ♥️ Suvretta!","time":"8 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
