gle.com/maps/contrib/106146265977922023941\">Grand Hotel Kronenhof Pontresina</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN37zcvogAjvu-wx5r85P8M0CFCGRQ3m2EGA3N_0wi6rljWn03osQEiWX7CylRmJVNgbI85L7XlLrfP0YP59JtTBMiD6hLSqeWN7bqQxSG7NHRxWrS89zjXnSworsNKhKpQ97RzovRMzHv9pECFUFOfNxMhSW1tfJ-Ec-vM7YJcfNTQd0sAv3h4y8vgvb13s35ye0LQ9TylI_Sdon0x9wWaMiqox4s73Z-9J1jj3BfWdeyua7U6lC7S_XR0kwEYgdtlYvvMuQ8if7W1wvexD1ej9MxX2x6DiNJZTRF6-CMatvw","width":1725,"height":2300,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/106146265977922023941\">Grand Hotel Kronenhof Pontresina</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN1ZhZvqvNS8MdERfOIWD2k8HTpe170d_oWGxpw4G7fbZsdkOH7mjqfCT7zUIc7a8nayWZ7t3vu0fnvvz1IikCZl6uNkfv2Asy8sEOlIP8U-MhCBD8BehsPRZnr65GYiTP64SGYa1sjdxUqw73LF0aII6oCiMpOhBXShhIz7C1k27Wq0K4K4si--RuiVsuLboCicWHVCQSoUjg6MA9eG4sBTqgIN_b4AgGBwYLqySB0-qM28M-s2ikcKJNC5lW75cikCIGyzZCRbGtx4rv_DNqLn1fVLQno3_Fh6qQ_YuDYlCQ","width":1533,"height":2300,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/106146265977922023941\">Grand Hotel Kronenhof Pontresina</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"Daniela Cardona","rating":5,"text":"We truly couldn’t recommend this hotel more—our experience was nothing short of extraordinary. From the moment we made our booking until the day we left, everything was flawless—the service truly deserves far more than 5 stars.\nAngel, Daniel, Celso, Matteo, Luciana, and all the lovely team members who helped us at the bar, restaurant, and in our room… you all made the Grand Hotel Kronenhof an unforgettable experience. This hotel will forever hold a special place in our hearts, as it’s where we got engaged. We couldn’t have imagined a more magical setting for such a life-changing moment.\nWords truly fall short when trying to express our gratitude or describe how highly we recommend this hotel. The facilities are impeccably maintained, the rooms are spacious, extremely comfortable, and spotless. Breakfast was delicious, the transport service (pick-up and drop-off) was absolutely 5-star, and the staff are incredibly polite and always delighted to help. They even assisted us in finding a ski school and made it even easier by arranging ski equipment directly at the hotel, ready to go.\nAbsolutely breathtaking from start to finish!","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"이우영","rating":5,"text":"This hotel was nothing short of exceptional.\nI stayed here from December 9 to December 12 and felt genuinely happy throughout my entire stay.\n\nThe staff demonstrated the highest level of professionalism and warmth, and both the facilities and the overall environment were outstanding. The views from the room, the lobby, and the swimming pool were absolutely breathtaking. The dining experience was elegant and refined, with a pleasant atmosphere perfectly suited to the dress code.\n\nAt every corner of the hotel, I was greeted with sincere smiles and kindness from the staff. From arrival to departure, the hospitality was consistently warm and welcoming, leaving me with a strong desire to return and stay here again in the future.","time":"3 weeks ago"},{"author":"DSB","rating":3,"text":"We have mixed feelings about our stay at this hotel. On the one hand, the property itself is beautiful, and some members of the staff were very friendly and helpful. On the other hand, not all personnel—particularly within the concierge service—seem to be properly trained. On one occasion, the employee we were speaking with was quite rude.\n\nWe also found it very strange that during our two-day stay we were unable to dine at either of the hotel’s two restaurants. One evening, one restaurant was booked for a private event, and we were informed of this in advance. However, in such a case, we would expect the other restaurant to be open exclusively for hotel guests and for the staff to ensure that guests are able to have dinner on the premises. The alternative dining options suggested by the concierge on both evenings were not very appealing; one of them, in particular, had extremely poor service.\n\nAs we were celebrating my husband’s birthday, it was especially disappointing that the staff was unable to arrange dinner within the hotel. This simply does not meet the standards of a five-star hotel.\n\nAdditionally, the coffee at this hotel is absolutely terrible, especially what is served at breakfast. We expected that a five-star hotel would invest in a proper coffee machine rather than serving cheap automatic coffee that is barely drinkable. The breakfast food presentation was also underwhelming, giving us the impression that the hotel is cutting corners in this area.\n\nOther than these issues, as mentioned, the hotel itself is very beautiful. However, despite this, we will not be returning.","time":"3 weeks ago"},{"author":"Rola Abusharaf","rating":5,"text":"This is one of the most beautiful hotels I’ve stayed in. The view, the rooms, the breakfast, the décor, and the overall atmosphere are all excellent. The concierge service is outstanding, especially Angel Blanco, who is truly amazing. Ask him about anything and he will give you the best advice. A wonderful experience—highly recommended!","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"Terri Choi","rating":5,"text":"⸻\n\nThe Grand Hotel Kronenhof in Pontresina is truly one of the best we’ve ever stayed in. Everything was flawless from start to finish. The room was spacious, beautifully designed, and offered breathtaking views. Yet what truly set this place apart was not just the comfort or scenery, but the exceptional staff. They were genuinely kind, attentive, and went above and beyond to make our stay unforgettable.\n\nWe were touched by the hotel’s generosity—fresh fruit delivered daily to our room and complimentary rides to train and funicular stations in the hotel car. Whatever we asked for, they did their utmost to provide.\n\nIn every aspect—location, luxury, cleanliness, amenities, and especially service—this hotel exceeded expectations. If it were possible, we’d gladly give it six stars.","time":"4 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
