iant. The view is also amazing. I would recommend this place, and we will definitely come back for sure if we get a chance to visit Lugano again. Thank you so much!","time":"2 months ago"},{"author":"Hanna","rating":5,"text":"My husband and I had the pleasure of staying at this beautiful and serene hotel to celebrate our 10th anniversary. The place is spectacular and so is the staff, who went above and beyond to accommodate us.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Adriana Iordache","rating":5,"text":"Top of the Top 🤩👌\nOur Holiday started because of the rain in Zürich 😅we started with 3 days and extended to 7 days.Being so long in the hotel we had several evenings in the restaurant, getting to know more of the employees.\nThe food is Top 👌🤩\nThe hole team very happy with the new manager Antonino , we like Customers also 🙏.\nI really highly recommend this restaurant ,\n1-for the best view ( the Best in Lugano ),\n2-Amazing Food Meniu\n3- Quality service\nBest regards and many thanks to: Luca the sommelier, Luca the handsome one 🤣, Massimo and of course Antonino 🤗\nUntil next summer 🥂🥳","time":"5 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
